en he turned quietly to his household, and brought forth a fat [roasted] calf,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4701.mp3","surahId":51,"words":[{"id":28813,"position":1,"arabic":"فَرَاغَ","translation":"অতঃপর সে চলে গেল","audioUrl":"wbw/051_026_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28814,"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَىٰٓ","translation":"নিকট","audioUrl":"wbw/051_026_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28815,"position":3,"arabic":"أَهْلِهِۦ","translation":"তার স্ত্রীর","audioUrl":"wbw/051_026_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28816,"position":4,"arabic":"فَجَآءَ","translation":"অতঃপর আনল","audioUrl":"wbw/051_026_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28817,"position":5,"arabic":"بِعِجْلٍۢ","translation":"একটি বাছুর নিয়ে (তাজা)","audioUrl":"wbw/051_026_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28818,"position":6,"arabic":"سَمِينٍۢ","translation":"মোটা তাজা","audioUrl":"wbw/051_026_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":28819,"position":7,"arabic":"٢٦","translation":"(২৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":27,"arabic":"فَقَرَّبَهُۥٓ إِلَيْهِمْ قَالَ أَلَا تَأْكُلُونَ","translation":"and placed it before them, saying, “Will you not eat?”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4702.mp3","surahId":51,"words":[{"id":29739,"position":1,"arabic":"فَقَرَّبَهُۥٓ","translation":"তা অতঃপর কাছে আনল","audioUrl":"wbw/051_027_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29740,"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَيْهِمْ","translation":"তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/051_027_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29741,"position":3,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/051_027_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29742,"position":4,"arabic":"أَلَا","translation":"\"না কেন","audioUrl":"wbw/051_027_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29743,"position":5,"arabic":"تَأْكُلُونَ","translation":"তোমরা খাচ্ছ\"","audioUrl":"wbw/051_027_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":29744,"position":6,"arabic":"٢٧","translation":"(২৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":28,"arabic":"فَأَوْجَسَ مِنْهُمْ خِيفَةًۭ ۖ قَالُوا۟ لَا تَخَفْ ۖ وَبَشَّرُوهُ بِغُلَٰمٍ عَلِيمٍۢ","translation":"[And when he saw that the guests would not eat,] he became apprehensive of them; [but] they said, “Fear not” - and gave him the glad tiding of [the birth of] a son who would be endowed with deep knowledge.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4703.mp3","surahId":51,"words":[{"id":30692,"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَوْجَسَ","translation":"ফলে তিনি অনুভব করলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30693,"position":2,"arabic":"مِنْهُمْ","translation":"তাদের থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30694,"position":3,"arabic":"خِيفَةًۭ ۖ","translation":"ভয়","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30696,"position":4,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলল","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30697,"position":5,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"\"না","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30698,"position":6,"arabic":"تَخَفْ ۖ","translation":"ভয় করো\"","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30700,"position":7,"arabic":"وَبَشَّرُوهُ","translation":"এবং তাকে তারা সুসংবাদ দিল","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30701,"position":8,"arabic":"بِغُلَـٰمٍ","translation":"একটি ছেলের (জন্মের)","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30702,"position":9,"arabic":"عَلِيمٍۢ","translation":"(যে হবে) জ্ঞানী","audioUrl":"wbw/051_028_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":30703,"position":10,"arabic":"٢٨","translation":"(২৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":29,"arabic":"فَأَقْبَلَتِ ٱمْرَأَتُهُۥ فِى صَرَّةٍۢ فَصَكَّتْ وَجْهَهَا وَقَالَتْ عَجُوزٌ عَقِيمٌۭ","translation":"Thereupon his wife approached [the guests] with a loud cry, and struck her face [in astonishment] and exclaimed: “A barren old wo